Typewriter
----------

Convert text to PDF.

Example:
	# Make a PDF calendar.
	cal -y | tw -o calendar.pdf

Project Features/Problems:
	- Fontconfig is the only runtime dependency.
	- Automatic page breaking.
	- Uses a custom TrueType parser and PDF builder.
	- Only ASCII characters are supported.
	- Only Monospace, TrueType fonts are supported.

Project Goals:
	- Switch to existing Truetype and PDF implementations.
	- Simple codebase that can be patched for additional features.
	- Support unicode characters.
